                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="img">
              <%= image_tag 'img1.svg', class: 'img-1' %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </header>
      <section class="sect about" id="block-2" data-section-name="how_it_works">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="img">
              <%= image_tag 'img2.svg', class: 'img-2' %>
            </div>
            <div class="desc">
              <h3 class="h3">No times to waste?<br>1 hour a day gives<br>the immidiate result</h3>
              <p>
                The idea is plain and simple: by doing something everyday you’re interested in you learn more about it
                and become better in it everyday.
                Sometimes it’s even enough 15 minutes daily what is about 8 hours per month to master a new skill. And
                it is not difficult to find 15 minutes every day to get closer to your dream, right? While in the metro
                or waiting for you pizza or whenever.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="sect about" id="block-3" data-section-name="features">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="desc">
              <h3 class="h3">Only best practices<br>curated by<br>industry specialists</h3>
              <p>
                Theory is theory, but practice is the key.We crafted in-app content in close collaboration with
                professional productivity trainers & coaches, scrum masters and successful businessmen
                to make our tasks & activities really efficient.
                So it’s not about good practices, it’s all about
                the best ones.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="img">
              <%= image_tag 'img3.svg', class: 'img-3' %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="sect about" id="block-4" data-section-name="blog">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="img">
              <%= image_tag 'img4.svg', class: 'img-4' %>
            </div>
            <div class="desc">
              <h3 class="h3">Don't know how to start?<br> The app gives some ideas<br>according to your profile</h3>
              <p>
                One of the biggest challenges in the beginning
                is the right start. We made a research involving more than 5000 respondents (aged 14 to 45)
                to identify what they would like to learn.
                So based on that data the app will offer you some disciplines, skills and subjects that might fit
                your profile.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
